title: Not a small commit but all needed to be done so I didn't branch off:
message:
Not a small commit but all needed to be done so I didn't branch off:
Youtube links back goes to list instead of black browser
NSFW thumbnails don't try to go to internet
Cancelable polling now works
Smaller chunks of json since 25 items may take too long to download
Improved post GC
Maximum of one polltasks as we can easily get into an infinite loop
Improved switching of subreddits (polling and images) since the requests can be canceledin code now
Reduced sleep time for threads waiting for same image to 100ms insead of 500ms
Switching subreddits doesn't clear image cache

-sgnn7

reduced download timeout to 20secs
